title: Interfering resonances in the F-19(a,p)Ne-22 reaction.

x4freetext: Interfering resonances in the F-19(a,p)Ne-22 reaction.
The 3 MV Van de Graaff generator was used
Eight surface barrier detectors situated at
172 degrees with respect to the incoming beam were
Targets of SrF2 evaporated on a solid backing were
used. Targets with the thicknesses of 10 mu-g/cm2 were
used for the energy less than 2300 keV and of
20 mu-g/cm2 for the energy more than 2300 keV.
